# >>> librarian-git managed (TODO 012.5 durable-markdown backup) >>>
# Files-authoritative model: the durable knowledge-primitive markdown (TODO.md,
# HANDOFF.md, NEXT.md, GOAL.md, GAMEPLAN.md, todos/, docs/) IS tracked (it is the
# source of truth). Everything below is a rebuildable projection, an
# un-mergeable binary, a lock, or build cruft -- never a source of truth, so it
# is ignored. Edit project-specific ignores OUTSIDE this managed block; `librarian-git
# init` rewrites only the lines between the markers.

# Librarian DB + locks + journal + operational transcripts (rebuildable
# projection / un-mergeable binary; NOT the four primitives -- those live in
# todos/ and docs/, outside .agent/).
.agent/

# The derived cross-project rollup + its sidecars and reindex lock (workspace
# root; un-mergeable binary, rebuildable from every project's markdown).
.agent/librarian-workspace.db
.agent/librarian-workspace.db-wal
.agent/librarian-workspace.db-shm
.agent/librarian-workspace-reindex.lock

